WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:09.300 --> 00:00:12.580
 The lion is the most predatory of animals 

00:00:12.980 --> 00:00:16.340
 It can be harnessed not by force but by intellect. 

00:00:17.800 --> 00:00:25.180
 The trainer first tames him with food, then subjugates and hides him. 

00:00:25.780 --> 00:00:34.180
 In the Lord's hand, there is always a whip to arouse fear in an animal and be able to protect it 

00:00:35.060 --> 00:00:44.580
 No stranger will dare to feed a lion. Only a person who knows the animal can do it. 

00:00:48.060 --> 00:00:55.660
 Leo is Sultan, and Vizier is his handler. 

00:00:59.040 --> 00:01:02.320
 The lion is the greatest ruler of the Empire, 

00:01:05.940 --> 00:01:14.940
 I, however, subdue the Great Padishah by using a whip of truth and justice. 

00:01:21.120 --> 00:01:23.640
 I rule the whole Empire. 

00:01:24.880 --> 00:01:28.580
 Because all decisions depend on me, 

00:01:29.580 --> 00:01:37.460
 even the Sultan's orders are invalid without my acceptance. 

00:01:48.080 --> 00:01:50.420
 Lord, Ibrahim Pasha arrived. 

00:01:54.385 --> 00:01:56.385
 Lord? 

